{"tid":846562,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"初戀失敗既經歷令我無辦法信任而家既伴侶","createTime":"2018-10-03T13:28:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T14:28:45.000Z","uid":140094,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"402d977da97d702a417cff397acd30bad2f26db1","tid":846562,"uid":140094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:28:25.000Z","msg":"初戀幾年前同我分手既時候 講左一句其實從來無鍾意過我 推翻哂以前既一切 <br />\n佢講既野對我造成左好大既傷害同陰影 一直唔敢再拍拖<br />\n直到今年先同左而家既男朋友一齊 我知佢好愛我 我都好愛佢 亦都知佢同我既EX係唔同既人<br />\n但我一直阻止唔到自己諗 將來既佢都可能會講同一番說話<br />\n加上我本身有抑鬱<br />\n成日自己一個諗諗下就喊得好勁 無辦法相信眼前既幸福係真實 亦都無辦法真正相信男友<br />\n好辛苦 係男友面前就笑 自己一個就喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都知好無謂但可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da15b652c4b2cee13b0c5cdd2bbfbed5dcc12c1","tid":846562,"uid":203774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:00:55.000Z","msg":"係咪你分佢佢先咁講喳<br />\n如果係 佢一時接受唔到先咁講姐"},{"pid":"cf2b20b22a4153f1be3d99ed036bb1c291ea3ce3","tid":846562,"uid":140094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9da15b652c4b2cee13b0c5cdd2bbfbed5dcc12c1","tid":846562,"uid":203774,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:00:55.000Z","msg":"係咪你分佢佢先咁講喳<br />\n如果係 佢一時接受唔到先咁講姐"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:02:26.000Z","msg":"係佢飛我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0bab86959d4143e6cdc72e6c99d0d841198b381","tid":846562,"uid":431,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T14:06:08.000Z","msg":"樓主 雖然我好同情你嘅遭遇<br />\n但你ok煩膠<br />\n希望你叫春還叫春 但唔好狂開post<br />\n謝謝"},{"pid":"80040e82cfcb25dd5f0dd194bec